data.description: NEW ROOF (2020), HVAC (2015), FRESHLY PAINTED 3/2 Corpus Christi Ranch Home located in the Village of Summerhill. (New Photos coming soon)  The SPLIT FLOOR PLAN provides comfort and privacy for you and your guests, with an open living/dining area that is ideal for entertaining. Your friends and family will enjoy the ENCLOSED LANAI as well as the ADJOINING BIRDCAGE and PATIO.  The kitchen has good cabinet space, GRANITE COUNTERS, Tile Backsplash, a GAS RANGE and plenty of counter space. The Primary Bedroom has plenty of room for a king-size bedroom set, a walk-in closet and its own ensuite bathroom!  Notable updates: 3 Solar Tubes, Roof Solar Vent, Roof Heat Barrier, 2018 Vinyl Floors and Laminate Flooring in Guest Bedrooms, Enclosed Lanai under heat/air, extended Bird Cage & Patio.  This home is perfect for snowbirds, as an investment/rental property, or simply a great place to call home. The Village of Summerhill offers plenty golf, shopping, swimming and more. Nearby: Glenview Champions Golf & Country Club offers fine dining and 27 holes of championship golf.  Saddlebrook and Hawkes Bay executive golf courses are also nearby. The Saddlebrook Recreation Center offers countless ways to enjoy your days - bocce, shuffleboard, tennis, pickleball, and horseshoes outside, plenty of cool air and billiard tables inside. The adult pool is also a great place to enjoy our warm, sunny days. The Saddlebrook Softball Complex is right next door.  For weekend fun, the polo fields provide hours of excitement every spring and fall.
